      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "B) SECTION_MISMATCH / OBJECTIVE_LOCKED\nclient drops stale objective mutations by module/runtime\nlogs MUTATION_DROPPED_STALE_SECTION audit\nretries flush with pruned queue",
